<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4719989>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 1–6. Adults of Asclerobia spp. 1–2. Asclerobia alexandrae sp. nov. 3–4. Asclerobia sinensis. 5–6. Asclerobia tchahabarella. 1. ♂, Paratype, Mugur-Aksy, genitalia slide 391.20. 2. ♀, Holotype, Mugur-Aksy, genitalia slide 390.20. 3. ♂, Majia Houzhuang, genitalia slide 387.20. 4. ♀, Erdao Lake, genitalia slide 457.20. 5. ♂, Lectotype, Bender Tchahbahar (NHRS-TOBI000004936, courtesy photographed by Tobias Malm, NHRS). 6. ♀ Paralectotype, Bender Tchahbahar (NHRS- TOBI000004937, courtesy photographed by Tobias Malm, NHRS)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4719989/files/figure.png" .

